l motorcycle or bicycle riding, water sports (paddle boating and sailing), duck shooting, and Portuguese bull-tackling bravado in the riding stable or arena. Booking online.\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["sleep"],["name=Pousada de Santa Clara-a-Velha - Santa Clara, Nature Hotel"],["url=http:\/\/www.pousadas.pt\/historicalhotels\/PT\/pousadas\/Portugal\/Alentejo\/SantaClara\/home\/"],["email=recepcao.staclara@pousadas.pt"],["address=Barragem de Santa Clara\n7665-879 Santa Clara-a-Velha"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone=+351-283 882 250 \/ 283 882 404"],["tollfree="],["fax=+351-283 882 402"],["hours="],["price="],["checkin="],["checkout="],["content="]]}]},"Its peacefulness is ideal for shooting, fishing, water sports or even for a rest in perfect harmony with nature. This nature hotel is very close to the Natural Park and Costa Vicentina, where the beaches are very appreciated and known.\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["Splurge"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["sleep"],["name=Pousada de Alvito - Castelo de Alvito , Historic Luxury Hotel"],["url=http:\/\/www.pousadas.pt\/historicalhotels\/EN\/pousadas\/Portugal\/Alentejo\/CastelodeAlvito\/home\/"],["email=recepcao.alvito@pousadas.pt"],["address=Castelo de Alvito\n7920-999 Alvito"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone=+351-284 480 700"],["tollfree="],["fax=+351-284 485 383"],["hours="],["price="],["checkin="],["checkout="],["content="]]}]},"Alvito is a village near the city of Beja (about 30 km of distance), in the past it was a very important location, having been home of a royal pousada.\nWith the restoration of an unusual 15th century castle in Alvito, the beautiful Pousada Castelo do Alvito was born.\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["sleep"],["name=Pousada de Beja - São Francisco , Historic Luxury Hotel"],["url=http:\/\/www.pousadas.pt\/historicalhotels\/EN\/pousadas\/Portugal\/Alentejo\/SFrancisco\/home\/"],["email=recepcao.sfrancisco@pousadas.pt"],["address=Castelo de Alvito\n7920-999 Alvito"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone=+351-284 313 580"],["tollfree="],["fax=+351-284 329 143"],["hours="],["price="],["checkin="],["checkout="],["content="]]}]},"In the former 13th century Franciscan Convent located in the heart of the historical centre of Beja, we find the impressive Pousada de Beja, São Franscisco. This luxury hotel in Beja combines the mystic monument with the needs of today's standards of well-being and comfort.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Connect"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Stay safe"]},"\nAvoid hot Sun in Summer.\n",{"type":"==","value":["Cope"]},"\nMonotony of the plains.\n",{"type":"==","value":["Go next"]},"\nMilfontes,Serpa,Mertola.\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["WikiPedia:Beja (Portugal)"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["isPartOf"],["Alentejo"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["outlinecity"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Dmoz:Regional\/Europe\/Portugal\/Districts\/Beja\/"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Commons:Category:Beja"]]},{"type":"{{","value":[["geo"],["38.033333333333"],["-7.8833333333333"]]}]